title: Ebro In The Morning - Healthy Habits and Holding Grudges
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 8/8/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio talking about establishing healthy habits, Irv Gotti, holding grudges, and Kanye V. Pete Davidson.

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning! 

Subscribe to "Summer Jam: Through The Years" - hosted by Laura Stylez!
